<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="astonishment-n">astonishment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'stɒnɪʃmənt/    美 /ə'stɑːnɪʃmənt/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>惊讶：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>To my astonishment</strong>, he was so impolite. 
令我惊讶的是，他竟然这样没有礼貌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He stared <strong>in complete astonishment</strong> at the child.  
他瞪着那孩子，完全惊呆了。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 3</footer></div></div>